        <p>You can contact our costumer support at any time of the day! We are open 24/7.</p>
        <p>Don't forget to exercise! </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <h6 class="text-uppercase font-weight-bold">Contact</h6>
        <p>7000 York Rd., Towson, MD, 20832
          <br />info@groupproject.com
          <br /> (123)456-7890
          <br /> (123)123-1234</p>
      </div>
    </div>
